This script for Greasemonkey http://www.greasespot.net/ can be used with
Iceweasel/Firefox to add the following features to the DDTSS pages:
 * links to the relevant pages on packages.debian.org and on
   ddtp.debian.net both for source and binary packages
 * character counter for the translation of the short description
 * (EXPERIMENTAL) button to join the lines fo the long description
 * removal of "http:" from the src of the iframe so that it isn't
   loaded over an insecure connection
